BT /F2 12 Tf 54 542 Td (Opening Script) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 522 Td (Good day. This part of GrocerEaseIMS is the Backup and Recovery module. Its purpose is to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 508 Td (protect the inventory database by allowing an administrator to create a full SQL backup,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 494 Td (restore a valid backup, view backup history, and download backup files.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 468 Td (Create Backup Script) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 448 Td (When the admin clicks Backup now, the system asks for confirmation. After confirmation, the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 434 Td (frontend sends a POST request to the backup controller. The controller calls BackupManager,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 420 Td (which exports all database tables into a timestamped SQL file inside the /backups folder. If) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 406 Td (the SQL file is valid, the system shows a success message and refreshes the backup history.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 380 Td (Restore Backup Script) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 360 Td (For restore, the admin can upload a SQL file or select a valid file from backup history. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 346 Td (system validates the file before allowing restore. Before changing the database, it creates) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 332 Td (a pre_restore safety backup. Then it executes the SQL backup into the MySQL database. If) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 318 Td (successful, the system shows the safety backup filename.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 292 Td (View History, Download, and Delete Script) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 272 Td (Backup history is displayed by scanning the local /backups folder. The table shows filename,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 258 Td (date, type, size, and validity status. The admin can download a backup through the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 244 Td (controller. Delete Backup is not included in the current implemented code, so I will present) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 230 Td (it as a missing or future improvement, not as a working feature.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 204 Td (Automatic Backup Statement) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 184 Td (Automatic Backup is not included in this reviewer because the requested scope is the manual) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 170 Td (Backup and Recovery module. I will not present it as part of the implemented workflow.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 144 Td (Panelist Answer Tips) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 124 Td (- If asked why backup is needed: It protects the database from accidental data loss or) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 110 Td (wrong changes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 96 Td (- If asked where files are stored: They are stored locally in the project /backups) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 82 Td (folder.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 68 Td (- If asked about delete: The current backup module has no delete endpoint yet; it is a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 54 Td (recommended improvement.) Tj ET
