BT /F2 15 Tf 54 626 Td (11. Possible Questions and Answers) Tj ET
0.85 w 54 607 m 558 607 l S
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 589 Td (Question                            | Answer                                                      ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 577 Td ( ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 565 Td (----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 548 Td (What is the purpose of backup and   | To save the current database state and restore it later if    ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 536 Td (recovery?                           | data is lost, damaged, or changed incorrectly.                ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 521 Td (Why is backup important?            | The system stores important inventory records. A backup helps ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 509 Td (                                    | recover products, suppliers, stocks, and other records after  ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 497 Td (                                    | mistakes or failures.                                         ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 482 Td (What happens when backup fails?     | The controller returns an error JSON response and the frontend) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 470 Td (                                    | shows a Backup failed SweetAlert message.                     ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 455 Td (What happens when restore fails?    | The system returns a restore error. If the safety backup was  ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 443 Td (                                    | created, the message includes its filename.                   ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 428 Td (Why should restore be restricted to | Restore can replace the entire database, so only trusted      ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 416 Td (admin?                              | administrators should be allowed to do it.                    ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 401 Td (Where are backup files stored?      | They are stored as .sql files in the local /backups folder.   ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 386 Td (How does the system know if backup  | BackupManager creates the SQL file, validates it, and returns ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 374 Td (is successful?                      | status=success with filename, size, and table count.          ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 359 Td (Why is automatic backup not         | It is not included in this reviewer because the requested     ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 347 Td (included?                           | module scope is manual Backup and Recovery only.              ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 332 Td (What are the risks of restore?      | A restore can overwrite current database data. A wrong or     ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 320 Td (                                    | malicious SQL file can damage records or structure.           ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 305 Td (How do you prevent invalid backup   | The code checks file existence, .sql extension, readability,  ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 293 Td (files?                              | non-empty size, and SQL-like content before restore.          ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 278 Td (Is Delete Backup working?           | No. Delete Backup is not implemented in the reviewed backup   ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 266 Td (                                    | code. It should be added before presenting it as a working    ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 254 Td (                                    | feature.                                                      ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 239 Td (What happens if a backup file is    | The controller returns HTTP 404 with File not found.          ) Tj ET
BT /F3 8 Tf 54 227 Td (missing during download?            |                                                               ) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 198 Td (12. Final Summary) Tj ET
0.85 w 54 179 m 558 179 l S
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 164 Td (The Backup and Recovery module is a practical protection feature for GrocerEaseIMS. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 150 Td (admin can create a full SQL backup, view available backup files, download them, and restore) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 136 Td (the database from a valid backup. The module uses BackupManager.php for the core database) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 122 Td (export and restore logic, controllers/backup.php for authenticated backend actions, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 108 Td (views/inventory/settings.php for the user interface.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 89 Td (The strongest safety feature is the pre_restore backup created before restore. The important) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 75 Td (limitations are that Delete Backup is not implemented, backup audit logging is missing, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 61 Td (the /backups folder should be protected from public access. For presentation, the module) Tj ET
